Name: Tidy Up
Effect: Target Battlefield. Remove all active Substitute/Shed Tail Decoys and Entry Hazards (ie. Sticky Web, Spikes, Toxic Spikes etc.). Increase User's Strength and Dexterity by 1.
Description: The user coordinates a quick and efficient way to clean up the whole place. No things scattered on the floor, no toys out of the toybox. Perfect for when visitors come over.
